### AGROESPACE — API smoke tests
### Open this file in VS Code with the "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
### and click "Send Request" above any block.

@base = https://jvmddidfxabdbtiscdop.supabase.co/functions/v1/make-server-0c561120
@key  = REPLACE_WITH_AGROESPACE_API_KEY


### 1. Health (no auth required)
GET {{base}}/health


### 2. Auth check — should return 401
GET {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products


### 3. Auth check — Basic auth (WooCommerce / Logicom style)
GET {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products?per_page=5
Authorization: Basic {{ "logicom:" + key | btoa }}


### 4. Auth check — query-string (WooCommerce convention)
GET {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products?consumer_key=logicom&consumer_secret={{key}}&per_page=5


### 5. List products (paginated)
GET {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products?page=1&per_page=20
X-API-KEY: {{key}}


### 6. Look up by SKU (only images, like Routs.txt)
GET {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products?sku=SKU-PVT-500&_fields=images,id,sku
X-API-KEY: {{key}}


### 7. Create a product
# @name createProduct
POST {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pivot Central Western 500m",
  "sku": "SKU-PVT-500",
  "description": "Pivot central WESTERN, transport et montage inclus, garantie 1 an.",
  "regular_price": "",
  "manage_stock": true,
  "stock_quantity": 3,
  "stock_status": "instock",
  "categories": [{ "name": "Pivots" }],
  "images": [
    { "src": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611040549344-f71005756038?q=80&w=1080" }
  ]
}


### 8. Granular update — stock_quantity only (uses createProduct's response)
PUT {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/{{createProduct.response.body.id}}
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stock_quantity": 7
}


### 9. Granular update — regular_price only
PUT {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/{{createProduct.response.body.id}}
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "regular_price": "275000"
}


### 10. Delete the test product
DELETE {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/{{createProduct.response.body.id}}
X-API-KEY: {{key}}


### 11. Create a category
# @name createCategory
POST {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/categories
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Pivots", "slug": "pivots" }


### 12. Update the category
PUT {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Pivots Centraux" }


### 13. Create an attribute
# @name createAttribute
POST {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/attributes
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Marque", "slug": "marque", "type": "select" }


### 14. Update the attribute
PUT {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/attributes/{{createAttribute.response.body.id}}
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Marque (FR)" }


### 15. Add a term to the attribute
# @name createTerm
POST {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/attributes/{{createAttribute.response.body.id}}/terms
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Western", "slug": "western" }


### 16. Update the term
PUT {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/products/attributes/{{createAttribute.response.body.id}}/terms/{{createTerm.response.body.id}}
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Western Irrigation" }


### 17. List orders
GET {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/orders?per_page=20
X-API-KEY: {{key}}


### 18. Create a customer
POST {{base}}/wp-json/wc/v3/customers
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client@example.dz",
  "first_name": "Mohammed",
  "last_name": "Benali",
  "billing": {
    "phone": "+213661391012",
    "city": "Adrar",
    "country": "DZ"
  }
}


### 19. Register a media URL
POST {{base}}/wp-json/wp/v2/media
X-API-KEY: {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source_url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611040549344-f71005756038?q=80&w=1080",
  "title": "Pivot Western",
  "alt_text": "Pivot central installé en Adrar"
}


### 20. Public — submit a quote (no auth)
POST {{base}}/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test REST Client",
  "phone": "+213661000000",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "product_title": "Pivot Central 500m",
  "message": "Demande de test"
}


### 21. Public — list blog posts (no auth)
GET {{base}}/public/blog


### 22. Public — bump view count on a seed post
POST {{base}}/public/blog/optimiser-irrigation-cereales-sud-algerien/view
